sources.description:
Dorian makes a deal with Henry to stay forever young, but every wild night leaves his portrait looking rougher while he stays flawless. As Dorian’s fame grows, so does the chaos around him—until his secrets catch up and the mirror cracks.

Original title: Dorian (2003)

Uncensored version: https://youtu.be/m8HQkuVeV6Q

Director: Allan A. Goldstein
Writers: Ron Raley, Peter Jobin, Oscar Wilde

Main cast:
Malcolm McDowell - Henry Wooten
Ethan Erickson - Louis / Dorian
Victoria Sanchez - Mariella Steiner
Ron Lea - Detective Giatti
Jennifer Nitsch - Bae Conick
Karen Cliche - Christine
Amy Sloan - Sybil
Carl Alacchi - James
Bronwen Booth - Trina Rouch

Genres: Horror, Thriller, Drama
Release date: April 23, 2003 
Filming location: Montréal, Canada
